%% Export : sequence_tour_halt.png
sequenceDiagram
    actor Operateur as Opérateur
    participant CTRL as Frontend opérateur
    participant API as FastAPI :8000
    participant TAB as cybel_lite tablette
    participant ENG as TourEngine
    participant SDK as RealRobot
    participant ROS as rosbridge
    participant TTS as CybelTTSBridge

    Operateur->>CTRL: ARRÊT TOTAL / E-Stop
    CTRL->>API: POST /api/tour/halt
    API->>ENG: stop()
    API->>SDK: cancel_navigation + emergency_stop
    SDK->>ROS: /poi stop + /path_follower/cancel
    SDK->>TTS: stop speech
    API->>TAB: POST /api/tour/halt
    TAB->>ENG: stop()
    TAB->>SDK: cancel_navigation
    API-->>CTRL: 200 OK
    CTRL-->>Operateur: Journal « Arrêt total effectué »
